data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: Due to COVID-19 travel restrictions, the Manpower Management Enlisted Assignments Branch will host a virtual roadshow to promote retention among Marines, July through August 2021. The virtual roadshow will allow Marines the opportunity to participate in interviews, reenlist, and discuss future assignments. (U.S. Marine Corps video by Lance Cpl. Hailey Music)
